Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Class MutableIidSet

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.MutableHasLongSet<InstrumentId>
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.MutableIidSet
public class MutableIidSet
extends MutableHasLongSet<InstrumentId>
A mutable version of an IidSet.

Our convention is to use such mutable classes in as few places as possible, and when we are finished putting in data, 'lock' it by wrapping it into a corresponding immutable class - in this case, IidSet.
